title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

manifest_analysis.title:
Broadcast Receiver (com.facebook.CampaignTrackingReceiver) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: android.permission.INSTALL_PACKAGES
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

"InAppPurchase_DescriptionText" : "Плаћање ће бити зарачунато на ваш iTunes налог приликом потврде куповине. Налог ће бити задужен за обнову у року од 24 сата пре краја важећег периода. Корисник може да управља претплатом а аутоматско обнављање може бити искључено у подешавањима налога корисника након куповине. Ако откажете претплату, и даље ћете имати приступ вашој претплати до краја времена за који сте већ платили. За више информација, молимо посетите наше {link_terms} и {link_privacy}."

"InAppPurchase_DescriptionText" : "התשלום יחויב בחשבון ה-iTunes בעת אישור הרכישה. המנוי יתחדש באופן אוטומטי, אלא אם כן החידוש האוטומטי יבוטל לפחות 24 שעות לפני תום תקופת המנוי השוטפת. החשבון יחויב בגין החידוש 24 שעות לפני תום תקופת המנוי השוטפת. המשתמש יכול לנהל מנויים ולבטל את החידוש האוטומטי על ידי מעבר להגדרות חשבון המשתמש לאחר הרכישה. למידע נוסף, עיין ב{link_terms} וב{link_privacy} שלנו."

playstore_details.description:
Get magazine cover quality for any selfie with just a few taps! Powered by FaceApp AI, the most advanced neural portrait editing technology. Improve your selfie or just have fun with gender swap, hair styling and other free amazing transformations.

Improve
• Perfect selfies with the Hollywood filter
• Change hair color and style
• Find your perfect beard/mustache style
• Add a beautiful smile
• Replace background with a single tap
• Try color filters, lens blur, and numerous other tools
• Apply perfect evening or day makeup (paid feature)
• Full-size Impression filters (paid feature)

Have fun
• Swap genders
• Let AI find your best hairstyle and color
• Change your age
• Add amazing tattoos
• Let AI find the best style for you
• Check out the Hitman, the Heisenberg filters and many other mind-blowing transformations

Privacy Policy

Online Tracking Opt-Out Guide
